WEBVTT

00:03:58.104 --> 00:04:00.422
into the technologies we're creating,

00:04:00.446 --> 00:04:02.899
like machine learning,
artificial intelligence,

00:04:02.923 --> 00:04:05.795
social media algorithms,
self-driving cars.

00:04:07.023 --> 00:04:08.722
There is much to ponder here.

00:04:08.746 --> 00:04:10.770
It's not just a philosophical argument.

00:04:10.794 --> 00:04:13.729
Is as important
a conversation as there is.

00:04:14.172 --> 00:04:15.759
So let's go.

00:04:16.392 --> 00:04:17.808
Sam Harris, welcome.

00:04:17.832 --> 00:04:20.601
SH: Thanks, Chris.
CA: Sam, let's start here.

00:04:20.625 --> 00:04:25.944
How can you build morality
out of mere reason and science?

00:04:25.968 --> 00:04:29.987
And perhaps you could even start
by defining what morality even is.